title: PPPP’s Sajid Ali Bhanban wins PS- 28 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarians’ (PPPP) Sajid Ali Bhanban has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-28 ,Kaharpur-3, by securing 59217 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Ismail Shah of the Grand Democratic Alliance, who bagged votes 54,839.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 57.32 %.
